This directory stores log files written by the application.

Files in this directory are gitignored.

Development: logs are written to stdout only (pino-pretty).
Production:  configure your process manager or log collector (e.g.
             PM2 log rotation, Fluentd, or Datadog agent) to capture
             stdout and route it here or to your log aggregation platform.

Future file logging:
  - Install `pino-roll` for automatic log rotation
  - Update src/config/logger.js to add a file transport
